elements.name: To test the submit order details

steps.name: User enters the username and password
click on the SW Merchandising Module
click on SW Data Entry dropdown
click on SW Style Initial Details screen
Select the IPO from the list "IPO1706.2"
click on Add combination button and enter combination names"Combo1" and "Combo2"
click on Submit order details button
Verify whether the Garment Size type field data is displayed or not
User enter the data in PO Qty field for combos
Enter the data in IPO% field in order details

name: feature to test Jiva design style initial details screen functionality
